Let me tell you about those Canadian roads. 'Round here the deer lay in wait
in the culverts. Your lights pick em up at the last minute and you silently
say, stay bambi, stay. Wont even mention the Elk and Bear X-ings. Well at
least the bears have sense enough to run in the opposite direction.
